On Thu, 3 Jun 1999, Chuck Lever wrote:
> 	 */
> 	if (find_vma_intersection(mm, oldbrk, newbrk+PAGE_SIZE)) {
>-		return -ENOMEM;
>+		ret = -ENOMEM;
